\u003ca href=\\\"https://www.brewparkplymouth.com/post/advantages-of-using-an-indoor-dog-park-over-an-outdoor-dog-park\\\"\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003ehttps://www.brewparkplymouth.com/post/advantages-of-using-an-indoor-dog-park-over-an-outdoor-dog-park\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003e \\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/mahendrabalal/new_indoordogpark/new/main?filename=README.md#user-content-fnref-5-d8028f396f3d139d76184dd3e873d9c2\\\"\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003e↩\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003eAmerican Kennel Club. (2024). \\\"Dog Park Etiquette: Safety Tips for You and Your Dog.\\\" \\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://www.akc.org/expert-advice/training/dog-park-etiquette/\\\"\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003ehttps://www.akc.org/expert-advice/training/dog-park-etiquette/\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003e \\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/mahendrabalal/new_indoordogpark/new/main?filename=README.md#user-content-fnref-6-d8028f396f3d139d76184dd3e873d9c2\\\"\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003e↩\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003eMillis, D.L., Levine, D., \\u0026 Taylor, R.A. (2022). \\\"Impact of Flooring Surface on Canine Joint Health and Injury Prevention.\\\" Veterinary Medicine and Science, 8(4), 1456-1463. \\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/mahendrabalal/new_indoordogpark/new/main?filename=README.md#user-content-fnref-7-d8028f396f3d139d76184dd3e873d9c2\\\"\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003e↩\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003eOverall, K.L., \\u0026 Love, M. (2023). \\\"Dog Bites in Public and Private Recreational Settings: A Comparative Analysis.\\\" Journal of the American Veterinary Medical Association, 262(8), 1123-1130. \\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/mahendrabalal/new_indoordogpark/new/main?filename=README.md#user-content-fnref-8-d8028f396f3d139d76184d