 pet care, and pet-friendly lifestyles. He enjoys researching and sharing helpful, easy-to-understand information that supports responsible pet ownership and helps readers make informed decisions for their pets. Through his writing, Bharat aims to educate and engage pet lovers with practical tips, insights, and well-researched content.\",\"url\":\"\",\"link\":\"/blog/author/bharat-thapa-magar\",\"avatar_urls\":{\"24\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/8713cd1871f637484fad5d88487bc635a6be491a-1170x2532.webp?rect=0,681,1170,1170&w=24&h=24\",\"48\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/8713cd1871f637484fad5d88487bc635a6be491a-1170x2532.webp?rect=0,681,1170,1170&w=48&h=48\",\"96\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/8713cd1871f637484fad5d88487bc635a6be491a-1170x2532.webp?rect=0,681,1170,1170&w=96&h=96\"}},\"categories\":[{\"id\":91382944,\"name\":\"indoor dog park\",\"slug\":\"indoor-dog-park\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/category/indoor-dog-park\",\"taxonomy\":\"category\",\"parent\":0,\"meta\":{}}],\"tags\":[{\"id\":5473141,\"name\":\"Climate control\",\"slug\":\"climate-control\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/climate-control\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}},{\"id\":53459804,\"name\":\"indoor dog park\",\"slug\":\"indoor-dog-park\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/indoor-dog-park\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}},{\"id\":90100489,\"name\":\"Pets care\",\"slug\":\"pets-care\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/pets-care\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}},{\"id\":75385452,\"name\":\"Urbans-dogs\",\"slug\":\"urbans-dogs\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/urbans-dogs\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}}],\"featuredImage\":{\"id\":10206235,\"date\":\"2025-12-31T01:00:44.198Z\",\"slug\":\"7-best-indoor-dog-parks-in-minneapolis\",\"type\":\"attachment\",\"link\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g